There are multiple reasons that change your facial symmetry. Lifestyle mistakes such as sleeping on your face squishes your face and changes the way your face appears on one side. It can cause droopy lips on one side of your face, more wrinkles on one side versus another. Chewing gum may be a good jawline exercise but it mostly develops one half of your Jawline which ultimately gives you a crooked jaw.
If you want to have a better looking face Not applying enough sunscreen while driving is not an option. It damages your skin on 1/2 of your face. It not only wrinkles one side of your face faster but it also causes more skin thinning, age spots. Adding face yoga exercises and face massage techniques is a great idea if you have ever thought about how to get a nice jawline evenly on both sides of your face or to naturally get a face lift to make your face more balanced.
I have shared multiple mistakes that change your facial symmetry as well as solutions to fix the problems.
Just by changing your sleeping positions, chewing habits, lifestyle and including face firming exercises on both sides of your face equally you can not only reduce facial fat, reduce double chin, develop a sharp jawline, Lift droopy eyes and change the appearance of wrinkles on your forehead.

title: Only 6 mins Increase Skin and fat on face. How to plump up face, tighten loose skin to be firmer.
description:
üëá Watch Short Clips for Facial Exercise & Massage. Subscribe to DN.Beauty SHORTS üëá
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCob1iz4g-HLi-W4lk21o2EA?sub_confirmation=1

üëá Watch Facial Exercise & Massage in English. Subscribe to DN.Beauty Natural üëá
http://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnY_CoUStl5Ci30mH-Tuo6w?sub_confirmation=1

How to tighten loose skin, plump up face make face look younger.
Increase skin and fat on face to be firmer, radiant and free from wrinkles.

Saggy skin, on both the face and body, is often associated with the loss of fat. 
The deterioration or reduction of collagen and elastin in the dermis are another cause of saggy skin.

You have to massage to restore the firmness by stimulating the deep muscles on the skin. 
It increase firmness and increase skin elasticity.


Let's get started.
Start by washing your hands first.

Step 1
Apply lotion or essence that absorbs quickly into the skin.
Do not use the cream will be too slippery. Will not be able to squeeze the muscles in depth.

Place a finger on the forehead, massage it up and down to loosen the muscle for 20 seconds.
Using your index finger and thumb, squeeze the forehead over 20 seconds.
Using your index finger and thumb, pinch the eyebrows for 20 seconds.
Place the fingertips on the forehead and drag up to the hairline 5 times.

Step 2 - Plump cheeks and raise the cheeks.
Squeeze the cheeks up to the temples 5 times.
Do the other side as well.

Step 3 - Fill in the cheek wrinkles and mouth lines.

Use your fingers to squeeze along the wrinkles starting from the tip of the chin to the wings of the nose 5 times.

Step 4 - Fill the hollow cheeks.
Squeeze your fingers from the corner of the mouth to the ears 5 times.

Step 5 - Increase a firm skin along the face contours.
Use your fingers to squeeze the tip of the chin to reach the ear 5 times.
Squeeze your fingers from the jaw to the temples 5 times.
Move inward and squeeze up to the temples 5 times.

Finished, always do it 1-2 times a day to increase the skin make it look radiant and firm.

Please click subscribe to the DN.Beauty Natural channel.

title: Lip Flip, Lip Filler and Anti-Wrinkle Injections with Robyn
description:
Robyn visited Dr.Saorlaith in our Belfast clinic for Anti-Wrinkle treatment, Lip filler and Lip flip treatment ‚ú®

Lip Flip - A lip flip is a popular non-surgical aesthetic procedure that uses anti-wrinkle injections to enhance the appearance of the upper lip. During a flip, anti-wrinkle toxin is strategically injected into the muscles around the upper lip, causing them to relax and slightly flip upward. This technique creates a fuller and more defined look.

Lip Filler - Lip fillers are one of the most popular types of dermal fillers for increasing the volume of your lips. Fuller, more plump lips have become one of the most popular treatments in medical aesthetics. Lip filler injections are a semi-permanent solution that help to enhance lips that have lost their shape, volume or elasticity.

Anti-wrinkle injections aka botox. Anti-wrinkle injections are used to lessen wrinkles in different parts of the face for both men and women, with the most common areas being the sides of the eyes, forehead, bunny and barcode lines. They also treat other parts like the jawline, chin, downturned mouth, lips, gummy smile, and eyelids.

Interested in any of these treatments? Contact our team for a complimentary consultation 0808 273 7663 or email edenmedicalni@gmail.com.

title: 9 Face Slimming Exercises‚ú®,Facial Exercises to Tone and Slim Faceüå∏
description:
Yoga is good for your mind, body and soul, but did you know it also does wonders for your face? Both facial yoga and the right facial exercises can keep your skin feeling young, firm and fresh. By carrying out regular facial exercises, you can work these muscles to improve blood circulation to the different areas of the face, replenishing the oxygen supply in the muscles and the skin. This will result in a bright complexion and beautiful healthy glow, as well as alleviating skin tightening and sagging. Performing face thinning and toning exercises frequently will keep your face looking fit in the long term. Furthermore, regular facial muscle exercises improve blood flow to the face and, supply your skin cells with nutrients leading to a stimulation of skin cell regeneration and wrinkle prevention.
Here are some of the benefits of facial exercises:
- Strengthens the muscles in your face.
 - Reduces the appearance of wrinkles.
 - Increases blood circulation to facial muscles.
 - Releases any tension in the face and neck.
 - Firms and tightens the facial skin.

title: beauty at every AGE
description:
I will be so blessed to look in the mirror and see that face in 2073!  So many of us (me included) are searching for anti-aging skincare, anti-aging skincare devices, and overall how to turn back the clock on our age.  However, a better sentiment is to simply figure out how to look our BEST at every age.  Healthy skin is a better goal in my opinion :)

Taking care of your skin, and knowing the products that will help you target your skin issues or concerns  are an essential part of any skincare routine.

Join my skintheusiasm over on:
Instagram (@thechristaevelyn)
https://www.instagram.com/thechristaevelyn/
TikTok (@thechristaevelyn) 
https://www.tiktok.com/@thechristaevelyn?

=====
SHOP some of my FAVOURITE products and posts here: https://shoplist.us/cevelyn
=====

-----------------------------
*Bought myself
**Gifted/PR
-----------------------------

Taking care of your skin, and knowing the products that will help you target your skin issues or concerns  are an essential part of any skincare routine. 

Taking good care of your skin does not require a lot of products + a lot of expense.  I prefer to keep my routines minimal, and focus on what my skin needs at any given moment in time. 

Subscribe to my channel to stay informed about minimalist skincare, and how to achieve your skincare goals whether you have combination skin, dry skin, oily skin, acne-prone skin, rosacea-prone skin, or aging skin.  My goal is to educate you on simple ways to bring balance to your skin.  DISCLAIMER: This video is not meant to replace professional advice from a doctor or a dermatologist, it is simply my own experience. 

xo Christa Evelyn

SUBSCRIBE: https://www.youtube.com/c/ChristaEvelyn

About me:
I have been through a lot of trial and error to find simple skincare routines that work best for my sensitive, combination, aging skin.  I am a skincare enthusiast with a Bachelor of Science degree + a Masters degree, and I simply want to apply my expertise in education and science to my passion i.e. beauty + skincare! I hope you enjoy my approach. 

DISCLAIMER: This description may contain affiliate links that help support my channel, and if you choose to purchase a product through these links I may receive a small commission. If you choose to use them, thank you for your ongoing support - it is greatly appreciated!

#beauty  #skincare  #antiaging

Welcome to my facial yoga channel.  In this channel, I show you how you can keep your facial skin young and beautiful by doing simple and inexpensive exercises.  Facial yoga is a natural and healthy way to maintain the beauty and youth of the facial skin.  By doing exercises that strengthen the muscles and skin of the face, you can prevent wrinkles, sagging, sagging cheeks and an unsightly nose.  These exercises also induce relaxation, improve sleep, increase self-confidence and prevent the need for surgery or botox.

 In this video, I teach you some useful facial yoga exercises that you can do anytime, anywhere.  You only need a few minutes and a mirror to start facial yoga.  So what are you waiting for?  Let's experience facial yoga together.

title: Facial Symmetry with Muscle Toning (energetic audio)
description:
Facial symmetry has been shown to have an effect of ratings of attractiveness in human faces. More symmetrical faces are perceived as more attractive in both males and females, although facial symmetry plays a larger role in judgments of attractiveness concerning female faces. A wide variety of methods have been used to examine the claim that facial symmetry plays a role in judgments of beauty.
The programming (energetic/morphic) works towards changing the symmetry of your face to make it more symmetrical and thereby make it appear more attractive.
It also directly working on toning and strengthening all your facial muscles.
Use as much as 3 times a day, remember this also works the muscles and they can become sore,
it may be a brand new thing in the world to have a sore face though?
Its also not gender specific. So for Unisex use.

As we age the skin's collagen and elastin begins to slow down and we start to see some pigmentation. We also start to see the effect of hereditary and environmental factors on the skin, your veins and bones can be seen more easily. Scratches, cuts, or bumps can take longer to heal. Years of suntanning or being out in the sunlight for a long time may lead to wrinkles, dryness, age spots, and fine lines. 

Regular practice of these 10 anti-aging facial massage techniques plumps the skin produce long-term changes in appearance. A small number of studies have tested facial massage techniques and suggest that anti-aging facial massage improves blood flow, plump the skin, or subjectively improve the appearance of the skin.

title: 4 Face Yoga Poses to Reduce Forehead Wrinkles | Natural Anti-Aging Tips with Priya Khandelwal
description:
Struggling with forehead wrinkles and frown lines? Wish you could achieve a smoother, more youthful appearance naturally? Look no further than the power of Face Yoga!

In this video, Face Yoga Expert Priya Khandelwal (@glowwithpriya_) unveils 4 effective yoga poses specifically designed to target forehead wrinkles and promote a radiant glow. This comprehensive routine incorporates The Wow Detox Combo, a unique technique that combines acupressure and gentle massage to detoxify and revitalize your forehead area. You'll also learn techniques to banish frown lines, master The V Pose for a lifting effect, and experience a relaxing Temporal Massage to release tension and promote overall well-being.

Here's what you'll learn in this Face Yoga for Forehead Wrinkles video:

‚úÖ The Wow Detox Combo: This innovative technique combines acupressure and gentle massage to stimulate circulation, eliminate toxins, and smooth out forehead wrinkles.
‚úÖ No More Frown Lines: Say goodbye to those unwanted lines between your brows! Priya will guide you through targeted exercises to relax the frowning muscles and prevent future wrinkles.
‚úÖ The V Pose: This powerful pose helps lift and firm the forehead area, leaving you with a more youthful and sculpted appearance.
‚úÖ Temporal Massage: This relaxing massage technique releases tension in the temples, contributing to a smoother forehead and a more refreshed look.

By incorporating these 4 Face Yoga poses into your daily routine, you can expect to see visible results in reducing the appearance of forehead wrinkles, frown lines, and overall tightness. Not only will your forehead feel smoother and more relaxed, but you'll also experience a natural glow and a more youthful radiance.

title: How to look 10 years younger: The secrets of anti-aging makeup!
description:
How to look 10 years younger: The secrets of anti-aging makeup!
In the quest for eternal youth, makeup plays a key role. The first thing you should pay attention to is the foundation. Light foundation products with a moisturizing effect hide imperfections without overloading the skin. Use concealer to mask dark circles under the eyes, making the look fresher and more relaxed.
Blush is your loyal ally! Apply them to the apples of your cheeks, choosing warm shades to add a healthy blush to your face. Choose soft pastel shadows for the eyes, and the emphasis on eyelashes and eyebrows will help create an open look effect.
Don't forget about the lips: gloss or light tints visually increase the volume. Complete the look with a light highlighter on the cheekbones and in the corners of the eyes ‚Äî it will give radiance and youth. By following these secrets, you can return to youth and self-confidence, making the world brighter and more beautiful!

title: Men‚Äôs Ultimate Facial Experience at Le Royale Space | Nairobi Grooming Vlog
description:
Join me on a journey through the ultimate men's grooming experience at Le Royale Space, Nairobi's premier spa located in Kilimani at Westfield Hub.  This video showcases a comprehensive facial scrub session, blending traditional techniques with modern skincare treatments.

What to Expect in This Video:

Warm Welcome: A friendly spa therapist greets me, setting the tone for a relaxing experience.

Skin Analysis & Cleansing: A thorough skin check followed by an oil and foam cleanse to prepare my face.

Gentle Exfoliation: Application of a gritty yet gentle facial scrub to remove dead skin and impurities.

Detoxifying Black Mask: A cooling black mask is applied to draw out deep-seated toxins.

Facial Massage & Hydra Facial: Post-mask, a soothing facial massage is followed by a hydra facial treatment to hydrate and rejuvenate the skin.

Steam Bath Session: A steam bath to open up pores and enhance skin absorption.

Body Scrub Teaser: A sneak peek into a relaxing body scrub session focusing on shoulders and arms.

Manicure Glow-Up: Finishing touches with a professional manicure, leaving my hands looking sharp.

Confident Exit: Leaving the spa feeling refreshed and confident. 


Ready to Elevate Your Grooming Game?

Call/WhatsApp: +254 737 327492

Email: leroyalespace@gmail.com

View Our Pricing: https://le-royalespace.co.ke/pricing/ 


Visit Us:
Le Royale Space, Kilimani, Westfield Hub, Nairobi, Kenya 

Follow Us for More Grooming Tips and Spa Experiences!

title: East Asian Beauty Standard is Messed Up
description:
The East Asian Beauty Standard is long known to be strict and rigid. In recent years with the rise of short-form TikTok videos and the popularity of social media, such standard has gotten even more unrealistic. This video criticizes the key features of the East Asian Beauty Standards. These features are:  

white& pale skin
large eyes (often with double eyelids)
Skinny: slim, delicate frame

Chapters:
0:00 Introduction to the 3 Major Beauty Standard
1:53 Standard 1: White, pale skin
5:24 Standard 2: Big eyes with Double Eyelids
7:04 Standard 3: Being Skinny 

The video concludes with contemplating the prospects of these standards in East Asia
